description:
I’m slightly freaking out but here we go: here’s the artwork (done by me) for our single As One. This song is fully composed, written and all instruments are played by my mega talented husband @johnambrosefuzz. I just sing haha. We have a very important message to share so please go check it out, it’s *F R E E* at bandcamp. It comes with a lyric sheet and a coloring page as well! Donations accepted. L!nk in b i o. 😊
